org.apache.ignite.internal.processors.cache

Class StoredCacheData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ignite.internal.processors.cache.StoredCacheData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class StoredCacheData
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Cache data to write to and read from IgnitePageStoreManager. In a nutshell, contains (most importantly) CacheConfiguration and additional information about cache which is not a part of configuration. This class is Serializable and is intended to be read-written with JdkMarshaller in order to be serialization wise agnostic to further additions or removals of fields.
